{"tid":751962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天出席城市論壇　兩無戴委任證便衣警全程監視　否認跟蹤","createTime":"2018-07-22T11:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T00:43:12.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8702df86bf1076eef19a8b0c07053c34950225","tid":751962,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:03:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陳浩天出席城市論壇　兩無戴委任證便衣警全程監視　否認跟蹤</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180722/s00001/863ef6fc05861e4069d68462bff0c067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F863ef6fc05861e4069d68462bff0c067.jpg&h=6fa1d3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之1 - 兩人被記者追問下，承認是便衣警員。（梁智康攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180722/s00001/864719e0075bcfb6b715990b521e8cdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F864719e0075bcfb6b715990b521e8cdd.jpg&h=3fc3b512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之2 - 兩無戴委任證便衣警，在場地圍欄外全程監視論壇過程逾一小時，直至陳浩天離開現場。（梁智康攝）<br />\n<br />\n政府擬藉《社團條例》取締港獨政黨香港民族黨，召集人陳浩天中午於維園出席港台節目《城市論壇》時，有兩名沒有出示警員委任證，惟佩戴耳機並與現場軍裝警員交談的便衣男子，在場地圍欄外全程監視論壇過程逾一小時，直至陳浩天離開現場。兩人其後被記者追問下，承認是便衣警員。<br />\n<br />\n記者於論壇完結後追問兩人身分，兩人齊聲否認跟蹤陳浩天，一名綠衣男子反問「我有跟佢？唔好玩啦」，另一灰衣男子聲稱是保障活動秩序良好，「我哋做緊觀察角色」、「睇下有無特別嘢」。兩人多番強調未有行使警察權力，但未有回應若不行使權力，又如何去保障活動秩序良好。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天出席城市論壇後表示，自己近一個月受騷擾，包括被警察跟蹤，亦被一些「無著制服，無戴證件，唔知道（身分）」的人跟蹤。陳浩天回應傳媒提問後，乘一輛客貨車離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180722/s00001/1532240647106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F1532240647106&d=TX7dcU1hfrmzBqCl9MW4zDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1a71606a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180722%2Fs00001%2F1532240647106&h=263d4267\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180722/s00001/1532240647106</a>"},{"pid":"7b86d3f841340ea9118efc08385a6a12c2a9c759","tid":751962,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"好柒"},{"pid":"b3f98040dfd30849db50bf7278fd5811a82fd8ad","tid":751962,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7b86d3f841340ea9118efc08385a6a12c2a9c759","tid":751962,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"好柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"啲黑警好心改下個look先"},{"pid":"a1ef91154b740924a2ad13ab64be5729e7c8ae6f","tid":751962,"uid":20227,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fcf09f23c8210a8ff91157244e708c3ebcc25f6","tid":751962,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc22d38c31cafc27f9dd7ed578391469edc4841","tid":751962,"uid":131691,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解呢個世界冇出產G片係用「20人傳媒bukkake顏射2黑警」做題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5702f6eed7fede4948bb43521c030c4ca495fc","tid":751962,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9aeae6191ca4c8703a669b2487bce6006d9a9e02","tid":751962,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p